		<h1><a href="http://www.greenhomebuildermag.com/mayjun2014-40.php">The Uncertain Nature of Real Estate and Climate Change</a></h1>
		<div class="homepage-tile__body__byline">
			<time>07.09.2014</time> | <span class="authors">				Green Home Builder			</span>
		</div>
		<p>Former HUD Sec.&nbsp;Henry Cisneros: "We can still avoid most of the worst impacts of climate change, and significantly reduce the odds of costly, catastrophic outcomes&mdash;but only if we start changing our business and public policy decisions today. Real estate leaders must be attentive, informed, and prepared to act."</p>
